{C84: Closed Ruy Lopez: Unusual White 6th moves} 1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Bb5 a6
4. Ba4 Nf6 5. Nc3 Be7 6. O-O b5 7. Bb3 b4 $146 {Black threatens to win
material: b4xc3} (7... Bb7 8. d4 d6 9. dxe5 dxe5 10. Qe2 Nd7 11. Rd1 O-O 12.
Be3 Qe8 13. Nd5 Bd8 14. a4 Na5 15. Ba2 c6 16. Nb4 Rc8 17. axb5 axb5 18. Qd3 Nb8
19. Bc5 Be7 20. Bxe7 Qxe7 21. Qd6 Qxd6 22. Rxd6 {Steinbacher,M (2290)
-Herbrechtsmeier,C (2320) Germany 1986 1/2-1/2 (51)}) (7... O-O 8. a4 (8. Nd5
Bb7 9. Nxf6+ Bxf6 10. Bd5 Qc8 11. c3 Ne7 12. Bxb7 Qxb7 13. d4 {1/2-1/2 (13)
Bronstein,L (2357)-Perdomo,L (2312) Olavarria 2005}) 8... b4 9. Nd5 d6 10.
Nxf6+ Bxf6 11. Bd5 Bd7 12. a5 Rb8 13. Bc4 Be6 14. d3 d5 15. Bxa6 Ra8 16. Bb7
Rxa5 17. Bd2 dxe4 18. Rxa5 Nxa5 19. Bxe4 c5 20. c3 Qb6 21. cxb4 cxb4 22. Qa4 {
Fontaine,R (2507)-Nyback,T (2563) Stockholm 2005 1/2-1/2}) (7... O-O 8. d3 $14)
8. Nd5 $14 d6 ({Inferior is} 8... Nxe4 9. d4 Bb7 10. Re1 $18) 9. d3 h6 10. h3
O-O 11. c3 (11. a3 bxa3 12. Rxa3 Nd4 $16) 11... Rb8 (11... bxc3 12. bxc3 Rb8
13. Qc2 $11) 12. Ba4 {White threatens to win material: Ba4xc6} Nxd5 13. Bxc6 (
13. exd5 bxc3 14. bxc3 Na5 $11) 13... Nf6 (13... bxc3 $5 {is an interesting
alternative} 14. bxc3 Nxc3 $11) 14. Qa4 bxc3 15. bxc3 Bd7 16. Qxa6 $4 {
weakening the position} (16. Be3 $142 $14 {is the best chance}) 16... Rb6 $19
17. Qa7 Bxc6 18. Be3 Rb7 (18... Rb8 $5 {might be the shorter path} 19. Bd2 $19)
19. Qa6 Qd7 20. a4 (20. Rfb1 {is not much help} Rbb8 21. Rxb8 Rxb8 $19) 20...
Rb2 21. d4 (21. Rfb1 {what else?} Rxb1+ 22. Rxb1 $19) 21... Ra8 22. Qc4 Bxe4 (
22... d5 $142 {secures the win} 23. Nxe5 dxc4 24. Nxd7 Bxd7 25. f3 $19) 23.
dxe5 d5 24. Qd4 c5 25. Qd1 Bxf3 (25... Ne8 {makes it even easier for Black} 26.
Re1 $19) 26. Qxf3 Ne4 27. c4 Rxa4 (27... Rb4 {might be the shorter path} 28.
Rfc1 $19) 28. cxd5 $4 {a blunder in a bad position} (28. Rxa4 Qxa4 29. cxd5 $19
) 28... Rxa1 29. Rxa1 Qxd5 30. Rd1 (30. Re1 {doesn't get the bull off the ice}
Nc3 $19 (30... Qxe5 $6 {is clearly inferior} 31. Bf4 Qd5 32. Rxe4 $17)) 30...
Qxe5 31. Bf4 Qe6 32. Re1 Rb4 33. Ra1 (33. Qe2 {doesn't improve anything} Bh4
34. Rf1 Bf6 $19) 33... Nf6 (33... c4 $5 {seems even better} 34. Be3 $19) 34.
Bd2 Rb3 35. Qa8+ Kh7 36. Re1 Qd6 37. Be3 (37. Qa2 {does not win a prize} c4 $19
) 37... Rd3 (37... c4 {keeps an even firmer grip} 38. Qa4 Qd5 39. Rc1 $19) 38.
Qa1 (38. Qa4 {cannot change destiny} Qe6 $19) 38... Qd5 39. Qb1 (39. Qa4 {
cannot undo what has already been done} c4 $19) 39... c4 40. Bd2 (40. Qc2 {
is no salvation} Ne4 $19) 40... Bd6 (40... Bc5 $142 {and Black can already
relax} 41. Be3 Bxe3 42. Rxe3 $19) 41. Re3 (41. Be3 $19 {there is nothing else
anyway}) 41... g6 42. Rxd3 Qxd3 (42... cxd3 $142 {and Black wins} 43. Qd1 $19)
43. Qb2 (43. Qxd3 {is still a small chance} cxd3 44. Kf1 $19) 43... Ne4 (43...
Ne4 44. Qb7 Kg7 45. Qb2+ Kg8 46. Be1 Qd1 47. g3 Qxe1+ 48. Kg2 c3 49. Qa2 Nd2
50. Qa8+ Kg7 51. Qe8 Qf1+ 52. Kh2 Nf3#) 0-1

