{B08: Pirc Defence: Classical System} 1. e4 d6 2. d4 Nf6 3. Nc3 g6 4. Nf3 Bg7
5. Be2 O-O 6. O-O c6 7. h3 Nbd7 8. Be3 Qc7 (8... b5 9. a3 Bb7 10. e5 Ne8 11. e6
fxe6 12. Ng5 Nc7 13. Bg4 e5 14. Be6+ Kh8 15. f4 exd4 16. Bxd4 c5 17. Bxg7+ Kxg7
18. Bd5 Bxd5 19. Nxd5 Rf6 20. Nxf6 Nxf6 21. Qf3 h6 22. Rae1 Rb8 23. Ne6+ {
Solomon,S (2404)-Froehlich,P (2397) Victoria 2004 1-0 (33)}) 9. Qd2 e5 (9... b5
10. a3 Bb7 11. Bh6 a6 12. Bxg7 Kxg7 13. Qe3 e5 14. dxe5 dxe5 15. Rad1 Rfe8 16.
Nh2 Rad8 17. Ng4 Nxg4 18. hxg4 Nf8 19. f3 Qe7 20. g3 Ne6 21. Kg2 Rd4 22. Nb1 c5
23. Rh1 Ng5 24. c3 {Anarkulov,A (2167)-Georgiev,V (2358) St Gallen 2008 1/2-1/
2 (42)}) 10. d5 $146 (10. dxe5 Nxe5 11. Nxe5 dxe5 12. Rad1 Be6 13. Qd6 Ne8 14.
Qxc7 Nxc7 15. f3 Bf6 16. Rd2 Be7 17. a3 b6 18. Rfd1 f6 19. Kf2 Rfd8 20. Rxd8+
Rxd8 21. Rxd8+ Bxd8 {1/2-1/2 (21) Drtina,M (2260)-Veselsky,J (2200) Trnava 1988
}) (10. dxe5 $5 Nxe5 11. Rad1 $16) 10... cxd5 $11 11. exd5 a6 {Secures b5} 12.
Rab1 (12. a4 $5 $11 {must be considered}) 12... b5 $15 13. a3 {Black has a
cramped position} Bb7 14. Rfd1 (14. Rbd1 Rac8 $15) 14... Nb6 $17 15. Bxb6 Qxb6
16. Qg5 (16. Nh2 Rfe8 $17) 16... Nh5 (16... Rac8 17. Qe3 Qxe3 18. fxe3 $19) 17.
Nh2 (17. Qe3 $142 $5 {has some apparent merit} Qxe3 18. fxe3 $15) 17... Nf4 $17
18. Bf3 Rac8 19. Ng4 (19. Nf1 $142 $17) 19... Rfe8 $4 {letting the wind out of
his own sails} (19... f6 20. Qh4 $19) 20. Re1 $2 (20. Nf6+ Bxf6 21. Qxf6 Rc4
$15) 20... Qc5 $4 {gives the opponent counterplay} (20... Qd8 $142 $5 21. Qxd8
Rexd8 $17) 21. Rbd1 (21. Ne4 $142 Qc7 22. Ngf6+ Bxf6 23. Nxf6+ Kg7 24. Nxe8+
Rxe8 25. c3 $14) 21... b4 $4 {with this move Black loses his initiative} (21...
f5 $142 22. Nh6+ Kf8 $15) 22. Ne4 $16 Nxd5 $4 {strolling merrily down the path
to disaster} (22... Qc7 23. axb4 Rf8 (23... Qxc2 $4 {A poison bait which
should not be taken} 24. Nxd6 Rb8 25. Nxe8 (25. Nxe5 $6 {succumbs to} Ne2+ 26.
Bxe2 Rxe5 $11) 25... Rxe8 26. d6 Bxf3 27. d7 $18) (23... Nxd5 $4 {That pawn is
poisoned} 24. Rxd5 Bxd5 25. Nef6+ Bxf6 26. Nxf6+ Kg7 27. Bxd5 $18 (27. Nxd5 $6
Qxc2 28. Qf6+ Kg8 $18)) 24. Ngf6+ Bxf6 25. Nxf6+ Kg7 $16) 23. Nxc5 $18 (23.
Nxc5 Rxc5 24. axb4 Nxb4 25. Bxb7 $18) 1-0

