{D00: 1 d4 d5: Unusual lines} 1. d4 d5 2. Bf4 Nf6 3. e3 c5 4. c3 Nc6 5. Nd2 Qb6
6. Qc2 (6. Qb3 c4 7. Qc2 Bg4 8. Ngf3 e6 9. h3 Bf5 10. Qc1 h6 11. Be2 g5 12. Bg3
Bg7 13. b3 cxb3 14. axb3 O-O 15. O-O Ne4 16. Nxe4 Bxe4 17. Nd2 e5 18. Nxe4 dxe4
19. d5 Ne7 20. Rd1 f5 {Johannesson,I (2368)-Ragnarsson,D (2347) Reykjavik 2015
1-0 (46)}) 6... Bg4 (6... g6 7. Ngf3 Bg7 8. Be2 Bf5 9. dxc5 Qxc5 10. Qb3 Qb6
11. Qxb6 axb6 12. O-O O-O 13. Bc7 Nd7 14. Nd4 Rfc8 15. Bg3 Nc5 16. Nxf5 gxf5
17. Nb3 Na4 18. Rab1 Nc5 19. Ra1 Na4 {1/2-1/2 (19) Sedlak,N (2582)-Georgiev,V 
(2572) Neum 2008}) 7. Be2 $146 (7. Ngf3 e6 8. Bd3 (8. dxc5 Bxc5 9. Bd3 Bh5 10.
O-O Bg6 11. Ne5 Nxe5 12. Bxe5 Bxd3 13. Qxd3 Be7 14. a4 O-O 15. a5 Qc6 16. Nf3
Rfc8 17. Bd4 Nd7 18. Ne5 Nxe5 19. Bxe5 Bd6 20. Bxd6 Qxd6 21. e4 Rd8 22. Rfd1
Qc7 {Szabolcsi,J (2402)-Vegh,E (2303) Hungary 2007 1-0 (63)}) 8... Rc8 9. a3
Nh5 10. Bg5 h6 11. Bh4 g5 12. Bg3 Nxg3 13. hxg3 Bg7 14. Nh2 h5 15. Nxg4 hxg4
16. Rxh8+ Bxh8 17. Qb1 cxd4 18. cxd4 Nxd4 19. exd4 Bxd4 20. Nf1 Bxb2 21. Ne3
Rc1+ {Gareev,T (2570)-Hammer,J (2457) ICC INT 2008 0-1}) (7. h3 Bh5 8. Ngf3 e6
9. Be2 Be7 10. O-O O-O 11. dxc5 Bxc5 12. Bd3 Bg6 13. Bxg6 hxg6 14. Rad1 Rfd8
15. Bg5 Rac8 16. Qb1 Be7 17. c4 dxc4 18. Nxc4 Qc5 19. Ncd2 Ne5 20. Nxe5 Qxe5
21. Nf3 Qa5 {Halak,M (2234)-Marzano,C (2166) Krakow 2014 0-1 (58)}) (7. dxc5
Qxc5 8. Ngf3 g6 $11) 7... Bxe2 8. Nxe2 e6 9. Nf3 Be7 10. Ne5 Rc8 11. O-O O-O
12. Bg5 cxd4 (12... Rfd8 13. Nxc6 Rxc6 14. f3 $11) 13. Bxf6 {White wins a piece
} Bxf6 ({Less advisable is} 13... gxf6 14. Nd7 Qb5 15. Nxf8 $16) 14. Nd7 {
White threatens to win material: Nd7xb6. White forks: b6+f8} Qd8 15. Nxf8 Qxf8
16. Nxd4 Nxd4 17. exd4 Bxd4 {White wins the exchange} 18. Qb3 {White threatens
to win material: Qb3xb7} Bb6 19. a4 Qd6 20. Rad1 Qc7 21. h3 g6 22. Qb5 a6 {
Black threatens to win material: a6xb5} 23. Qd3 Ba7 24. Rfe1 Bb8 25. g3 h5 (
25... Qb6 26. Rb1 $11) 26. h4 Qa5 $4 (26... Ba7 $142 $14 {was a good chance to
save the game}) 27. Rxe6 $3 $18 {very forceful play.} Kg7 (27... fxe6 28. Qxg6+
Kf8 (28... Kh8 29. Qh6+ Kg8 30. Qxe6+ {Combination}) 29. Qf6+ Ke8 (29... Kg8
30. Qxe6+ {Combination}) 30. Qxe6+ {Double attack}) 28. Qd4+ Kg8 29. Re7 (29.
Re7 Qd8 30. Qf6 $18) 1-0

