{D02: 1 d4 d5 2 Nf3 sidelines, including 2...Nf6 3 g3 and 2...Nf6 3 Bf4} 1. d4
d5 2. Nf3 Nf6 3. Bf4 h6 $146 {Covers g5} (3... Nbd7 4. Nc3 (4. e3 c5 5. c3 Qb6
6. Qc2 g6 7. Nbd2 Bg7 8. h3 O-O 9. Be2 Ne4 10. O-O Nxd2 11. Qxd2 Nf6 12. b4 Ne4
13. Qb2 a5 14. a3 Bf5 15. Rfb1 cxb4 16. cxb4 axb4 17. axb4 Nd6 18. Rc1 Rxa1 {
Sahovic,D (2450)-Skembris,S (2400) Vrnjacka Banja 1982 1/2-1/2 (31)}) 4... c6
5. e3 e6 6. Bd3 Bb4 7. O-O h6 8. Qe2 O-O 9. e4 Bxc3 10. bxc3 dxe4 11. Bxe4 Nxe4
12. Qxe4 Nf6 13. Qd3 Nd5 14. Bd2 Ne7 15. Rfe1 Ng6 16. Ne5 Nxe5 17. Rxe5 f6 18.
Re3 {Lasker,E-Chigorin,M St Petersburg 1896 1-0 (55)}) (3... g6 4. c3 Bg7 5. e3
(5. h3 O-O 6. Nbd2 b6 7. e3 c5 8. b4 Bb7 9. bxc5 bxc5 10. Qa4 Nbd7 11. Be2 Ne4
12. Nxe4 dxe4 13. Nd2 cxd4 14. cxd4 e5 15. dxe5 Nxe5 16. Bxe5 Bxe5 17. Rd1 Qe8
{1/2-1/2 (17) Dresen,U (2300)-Brueckner,T (2345) Germany 1987}) 5... O-O 6.
Nbd2 b6 7. Bd3 Bb7 8. O-O c5 9. Qe2 e6 10. h3 Qe7 11. a3 Nfd7 12. e4 Re8 13.
Rfe1 cxd4 14. cxd4 dxe4 15. Nxe4 Nf6 16. Nd6 Rd8 17. Nxb7 Qxb7 18. Rac1 {
Szekely,P (2465)-Beliavsky,A (2645) Hungary 1998 1/2-1/2}) (3... Nh5 4. Be3 c6
5. g3 Bf5 6. Nbd2 h6 7. Bg2 Qb6 8. Qc1 Nd7 9. O-O e6 10. c4 Be7 11. h3 Nhf6 12.
Re1 a5 13. a3 a4 14. Bf4 O-O 15. g4 Bh7 16. c5 Qa7 17. Ne5 Nxe5 18. Bxe5 {
Tologontegin,S (2354)-Mandiza,F (2388) Tromso 2014 1-0 (76)}) 4. e3 Bf5 5. Nc3
e6 6. h3 {Prevents intrusion on g4} (6. Bd3 Bxd3 7. cxd3 Nc6 $14) 6... Bb4 $11
7. a3 Bxc3+ 8. bxc3 Ne4 9. c4 (9. Qb1 b6 $11) 9... b6 (9... g5 $5 10. Bh2 c5
11. cxd5 exd5 12. Bb5+ Nd7 $11) 10. Bd3 $14 O-O 11. O-O Nd7 (11... dxc4 12.
Bxc4 Nd7 13. Bd3 $14) 12. Bxe4 (12. cxd5 $5 exd5 13. c4 $16) 12... Bxe4 13.
cxd5 Bxd5 {Opposite coloured bishops appeared} 14. Re1 Nf6 (14... Qf6 15. c4
Bb7 16. Rc1 $11) 15. Ne5 $14 Rc8 16. c4 Ba8 17. Rc1 c5 18. dxc5 (18. Re2 Qe7
$11) 18... Rxc5 19. Qa4 {White threatens to win material: Qa4xa7} (19. Qb3 Qe7
$11) 19... Qe7 (19... Qc7 20. Nd3 Qc6 21. Qxc6 Rxc6 22. f3 $11) 20. Red1 Qb7 (
20... Rfc8 $5 $11) 21. f3 $14 {Prevents intrusion on e4+g4} Ra5 {Black
threatens to win material: Ra5xa4} 22. Qb4 Rc8 23. Rd3 (23. e4 Nh5 24. Bh2 Nf6
$16) 23... Rac5 (23... Nd5 $5 {is noteworthy} 24. Qd2 Qc7 $14) 24. Rcd1 $16 a5
$2 (24... Re8 25. Rd8 Qe7 26. R8d4 $16) 25. Qa4 (25. Rd8+ $142 Ne8 26. Qa4 b5
27. cxb5 Kh7 $18) 25... Qa6 $4 {causes even greater problems} (25... Qe7 $142
$16) 26. Rd8+ $18 Kh7 27. Qc2+ g6 (27... Ne4 {does not save the day} 28. R1d4
Rxd8 29. Rxd8 $18) 28. Qd3 (28. R1d7 Nxd7 29. Rxd7 Be4 30. Qxe4 Rg8 31. Rxf7+
Kh8 32. Qd4 Rg7 33. Nxg6+ Kg8 34. Rxg7#) 28... Bc6 $4 {Black crumbles in face
of a dire situation} (28... Rd5 29. Rxd5 exd5 $18) 29. Qd6 Rxd8 30. Qxd8 Kg7 (
30... Qa8 {a last effort to resist the inevitable} 31. Qxf6 Qf8 32. Nxc6 Qg7
33. Qxg7+ Kxg7 34. Be5+ f6 35. Rd7+ Kg8 36. Ne7+ Kf8 37. Bxf6 Ke8 $18) 31. Qe7
(31. Bxh6+ Kxh6 32. Qh8+ Kg5 33. Nxf7+ Kf5 34. g4+ Nxg4 35. hxg4#) 31... Be8
32. Rd8 Nd7 (32... Qxc4 {doesn't get the cat off the tree} 33. Rxe8 Qf1+ 34.
Kxf1 Rc1+ 35. Ke2 Rc2+ 36. Kd1 Rc1+ 37. Kxc1 Nxe8 38. Qxf7+ Kh8 39. Nxg6#) 33.
Qxe8 (33. Qxe8 Nf8 34. Qxf8+ Kf6 35. Qxf7#) 1-0

