fight} (8... O-O 9. Bg5 Be7 10. Bxe7 Qxe7 11. Nbd2 $18) 9. Kf1 dxc2 10. Qxc2
Nd4 (10... O-O {hardly improves anything} 11. Nc3 d6 12. Bg5 $18) 11. Nxd4 Bxd4
12. Bxf7+ $1 {Double attack: d4/f7.} Kxf7 13. Qc4+ Ke8 (13... d5 {desperation}
