Ne4 $18) 15. Nc3 c6 16. Ne4 Kd8 (16... h6 {the only chance to get some
counterplay} 17. Kg1 b6 $18) 17. Bg5 Rf8+ 18. Kg1 (18. Kg1 Qxg5 19. Nxg5 $18)
1-0

